answer_md:
You have to register `A` to the metaclass as well.

One way you can achieve that is by passing the metaclass to the parent class as well:
```python
class Abstract1(ABC):
    pass

class DecoMeta(ABCMeta):
    pass

class A(Abstract1, metaclass=DecoMeta):
    def fun1(self):
        pass

    def fun2(self):
        pass

